{"tid":1519840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"End你老母game呀","createTime":"2019-08-30T16:04:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T17:14:09.000Z","uid":158559,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1baccb609621c429f32fcd040f6d0f86e556a7c4","tid":1519840,"uid":158559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:04:27.000Z","msg":"全撚部人喺度吹撚到聽日一戰定生死咁<br />\n覺得聽日話最後嘅你哋喺咪<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傻撚咗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n我哋而家仲喺打緊Infinity War咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋當9月1機場死㗎？10月1唔撚洗送大禮慶祝鄰國國慶呀？<br />\n<br />\n聽日極其量喺呢次抗爭入面其中一場重要一役<br />\n唔撚該啱啱晚餐po班蛋散同我嘔撚返你哋個最後晚餐出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n係未做到之前 無人有資格去決定邊場喺End Game<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54823045a0f084b2fa3495469e361736fbdad8ca","tid":1519840,"uid":99904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:05:00.000Z","msg":"大家十一一齊去落佢面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0ab56ef28c1612d2a47b612d4066f1deb03efdc","tid":1519840,"uid":285371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:05:03.000Z","msg":"聽日唔係最後一戰，我地要長期戰等人權民主法案"},{"pid":"b79b878f8441c6f2e78b9c38bc493a8e769cae4a","tid":1519840,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">求入來推po！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n(極正經) 關注被控義士請快D碌入來！！！ 更新了整合名單，一個也不能少不只是口號！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1518567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1518567</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0b7177833a83cf2121ea6e58fa837b7bd94ef7c9","tid":1519840,